reviewText: This is a DVD that I could watch many times. Very thought provoking and educational.
Not as good as some others I've seen, however it is good enough to be in my collection.  Try " The Book of Ruth" that is a better one.

This is an excellent DVD that has beautiful scenery of the Holy Land, including all of the special tourist sites, worship music, culture and the story of Jesus.  I highly recommend this DVD to all Christians.
Wonder series and every church and home should have a copy or two,
I love this film, a simple presentation of life in Jesus' time here on earth!

Very well made documentary of the times when Jesus walked in Israel.  It leads you trough scripture always pointing to the Gospel of our Lord Jesus. You will get a clear picture of the daily life in that time period.
Diversified pictures and great scenery keep the movie interesting from beginning to end.
I highly recommend it.

Beautiful scenery and setting along with customs of that time in history make this film get five stars for me. It is very well made and has pace to keep your interest. You get a clearer picture of scripture when you know more about daily life in that time period. Highly recommend.
Praise be to God. I loved this. thank you.
This was so awesome, i really enjoyed it! What a pleasure to watch during Shabbat! Thank you so much for making this delightful depiction of the life of our ancestors and our King Yeshua!
Gives a better understanding of the Times of Jesus
Just OK.  There are many other better products out there.
Great price for a great DVD.
